value: Breeds irregularly in northern Russia (Onega River, Kirov, Perm Urals) and across Siberia to the Pacific Ocean, north to 60Â° N. along the Ob River and 65Â° N. on the Vilyuy River, east to Kamchatka, Kuril Islands, Sakhalin, Hokkaido, and Honshu, and south to Tyumen', Tomsk, the northern foothills of the Altai, Transbaikalia, Manchuria, and northern Korea. Migrates through China to eastern Nepal, northern India, Bangladesh, Burma, Andaman and Nicobar Islands, Thai- land, Indochina, Malaysia, and Indonesia.
